{"tid":942870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#111: 蒸巴出pool大作戰","createTime":"2018-12-16T06:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T06:25:28.000Z","uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2670a3775580ad4f42bfa4714748975cc38e5709","tid":942870,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n「西野七瀬世界第一」</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dX0wleA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdX0wleA.jpg&h=a7d798b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生、二期與三期生在內，團體目前共有40名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=CKAMKtmgZZ4JHF8XMmphFgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ae077563\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 北野日奈子ファースト写真集 「空気の色」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">12月27日正式發售</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gPlzise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgPlzise.jpg&h=379fa89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 井上小百合ファースト写真集 「存在」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cdBjIT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcdBjIT6.jpg&h=c461748b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 22ndシングル<br />\n「帰り道は遠回りしたくなる」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2GkiUls.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2GkiUls.jpg&h=a5ad3116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 22ND VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gMdCF81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgMdCF81.jpg&h=a26255e3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46 四期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjUnHMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNjUnHMj.jpg&h=61687ed4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=CKAMKtmgZZ4JHF8XMmphFgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6810576f\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\nNONE<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DeKaeueV4AA2r6Z.jpg:small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDeKaeueV4AA2r6Z.jpg%3Asmall&h=1fb35282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=CKAMKtmgZZ4JHF8XMmphFgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=cee83111\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"aae1fee29a6ac4ff5d8b989b28a408f8b6689378","tid":942870,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCjjn3O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCjjn3O.gif&h=5c42f36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金庸七瀬留名"},{"pid":"6829b725980f2384f5cb790eafe0ed77c6fe555a","tid":942870,"uid":63295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"111完又111<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590a164ec83febdd8dd225443d68fdef7adc3aeb","tid":942870,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6829b725980f2384f5cb790eafe0ed77c6fe555a","tid":942870,"uid":63295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"111完又111<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"諗緊重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc2f36b904545226eaadeebf2ae2c07d9000ada","tid":942870,"uid":63295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首席梅推強勢留名</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgGE7v3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgGE7v3.png&h=50fc4fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4期封面嗰本雜誌 海天出咗代購未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef08cd3b8dcd2d721873913996e1cd636db86c5","tid":942870,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"呢d一定要重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e9ba6ac97743d948a2034ef2bca63822685b9b","tid":942870,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"乃木坂46討論區#112: 蒸巴出pool大作戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/942876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/942876</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}